  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Professional development0Researcher Connect Year 3</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This programme builds the capacity to communicate research. Researchers need to publish articles to ensure their research findings are shared and to support their future careers. Researcher Connect involves a series of facetoface training modules, delivered by experienced trainers and backed up with online resources.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To build the communication skills of researchers in partner countries. Target: 800 researchers directly trained over 4 years; a pool of 20 local trainers established to ensure a strong train the trainer programme.</narrative>
  </description>
